=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104kem1665702731596.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/kem1665702731596.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/kem1665702731596.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"kem1665702731596\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      time as timestamp\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Map times to timestamps.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"kem1665702731596__topic_d54734e1_d54735e1_d54736e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kem1665702731596__p_d54737e1_d54738e1_d54739e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">USYS$ODx_PARAMS time as timestamp : on</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">off</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kem1665702731596__section_ax4_jtm_jcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d262684e63\">Arguments</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"kem1665702731596__ul_lds_jtm_jcc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"kem1665702731596__li_d25253e1_d25254e1_d25255e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kem1665702731596__p_d54743e1_d54744e1_d54745e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">on</code>—times will be mapped to\n                  timestamps (the default)</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"kem1665702731596__li_d25256e1_d25257e1_d25258e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kem1665702731596__p_d54746e1_d54747e1_d54748e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">off</code>—times will not be mapped to\n                  timestamps</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kem1665702731596__section_tbf_ktm_jcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d262684e88\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kem1665702731596__p_d54752e1_d54753e1_d54754e1\">The <code class=\"ph codeph\">time as timestamp</code> option\n            specifies how times are mapped.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529178\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529178\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "time as timestamp Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Aug 13, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 time as timestamp Map times to timestamps. USYS$ODx_PARAMS time as timestamp : on | off Arguments on —times will be mapped to timestamps (the default) off —times will not be mapped to timestamps Description The time as timestamp option specifies how times are mapped. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}